best fit, and best price find a donor bus with good pieces same year and
model (westy, deluxe etc)

> For the pas rear corner, should I have a used one cut from a donor? I
> seen larger, more complicated replacement pieces simply not fit well.

good used from a place like BustedBus or spend the $$ for new parts

Bus Depot has most if not all of the pieces you need. as you said he
doesn't make em only sells em and the fit can be hit or miss.

let us know where you got which and how they fit

